_sText:
DE_ASYLUM by G4AMER (released February 2012)

This is a map I made a long time ago. It is one of my favorite maps of mine. Small and fast paced, but with plenty of options to get to either of the 2 bombs sites. As always I hope you enjoy playing on this map as much as I did in creating it.

Couple of small places, some transitions and underground parking... it will be difficult to get lost! :-) Radar and Navigation Mesh for Bots in existence.

Happy Frags and Good Luck!
